snippet.title: 36 Days of Demonetization: People Standing in Queues at Banks and ATMs across the Country

localized.description:
36 Days of Demonetization: People are standing in queues outside banks and ATMs across the country. Hundreds of crores have been seized in income tax raids across the country after demonetisation. On the other hand people are struggling to withdraw cash even after waiting for hours in queues outside banks and ATMs.
